                    <td class="forumAlternate" >I am also a big fan of planned adds.  What I do in that situation is dependent on the dungeon layout.

If the dungeon is open (no doors), as soon as you get the &quot;mez has worn off message&quot;, position yourself to be looking down the direction from which they are coming.  As soon as you see them come within 4 seconds or so of your group (you may have to position yourself around corners to do this), start mez and bring them on in.  That is, run towards them in range, start mez, then start running ...</td>
